<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:02
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='411840' id='t-411840'>And with that understanding,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='414840' id='t-414840'>you should have witnessed,
in fact, part of you were,</span>
