<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='757400' id='t-757400'>over the next five years
that are the urgent five years.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='762640' id='t-762640'>But I do believe</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='765520' id='t-765520'>that we have come over the past six years</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='768480' id='t-768480'>from the impossible</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='770440' id='t-770440'>to the now unstoppable.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='772560' id='t-772560'>And how did we do that?
By injecting transformational optimism</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='777640' id='t-777640'>that allowed us to go
