<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='790579' id='t-790579'>and we can merge them harmoniously.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:23
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='792840' id='t-792840'>And as I look forward
to other global issues</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='796600' id='t-796600'>that will require
our attention this century --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='800480' id='t-800480'>food security, water security,
home security, forced migration --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='807080' id='t-807080'>I see that we certainly do not know</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='809520' id='t-809520'>how we are going to solve
those problems yet.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='813080' id='t-813080'>But we can take a page
