<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='830400' id='t-830400'>and that your loss is my gain.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='832640' id='t-832640'>Well, now that we're in a world</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='834760' id='t-834760'>in which we have reached
